{"jsonrpc":"2.0","method":"session/update","params":{"sessionId":"019d4438-400e-7661-b283-c84db8e24803","update":{"sessionUpdate":"tool_call","toolCallId":"call_X4vpJ6V0XEDuF5rmaDwKaPB5","title":"Read globals.css","kind":"read","status":"in_progress","locations":[{"path":"/tmp/orchestra-workspaces/ws-1774964648433-svlpcp/app/globals.css"}],"rawInput":{"call_id":"call_X4vpJ6V0XEDuF5rmaDwKaPB5","process_id":"43056","turn_id":"019d4438-401f-7133-9a7b-e968f581165b","command":["/bin/bash","-lc","sed -n '1,260p' app/globals.css"],"cwd":"/tmp/orchestra-workspaces/ws-1774964648433-svlpcp","parsed_cmd":[{"type":"read","cmd":"sed -n '1,260p' app/globals.css","name":"globals.css","path":"app/globals.css"}],"source":"unified_exec_startup"}}}}
{"jsonrpc":"2.0","method":"session/update","params":{"sessionId":"019d4438-400e-7661-b283-c84db8e24803","update":{"sessionUpdate":"tool_call_update","toolCallId":"call_IUtSnyVGFKxJIZGHnZgEYmF8","status":"completed","rawOutput":{"call_id":"call_IUtSnyVGFKxJIZGHnZgEYmF8","process_id":"26643","turn_id":"019d4438-401f-7133-9a7b-e968f581165b","command":["/bin/bash","-lc","sed -n '1,260p' README.md"],"cwd":"/tmp/orchestra-workspaces/ws-1774964648433-svlpcp","parsed_cmd":[{"type":"read","cmd":"sed -n '1,260p' README.md","name":"README.md","path":"README.md"}],"source":"unified_exec_startup","stdout":"# Szechuan Royale Chinese Restaurant Website\n\nA production-ready restaurant website built with Next.js 16, TypeScript, and Tailwind CSS.\n\n## 🏮 Features\n\n- **Mobile-first responsive design** with sticky navigation\n- **Full sections**: Hero, Menu Highlights, Online Ordering CTA, About, Location & Hours, Contact, Footer\n- **Szechuan Chinese aesthetic**: Imperial Red & Dynasty Gold color palette\n- **SEO optimized**: Meta tags, Open Graph, JSON-LD Restaurant schema\n- **Static export** for easy deployment to any hosting platform\n- **Google Fonts**: Noto Serif SC, Noto Sans SC, IM Fell English\n\n## 🚀 Getting Started\n\n```bash\n# Install dependencies\nnpm install\n\n# Run development server\nnpm run dev\n\n# Build for production (static export)\nnpm run build\n\n# The static site is generated in the `out/` directory\n```\n\n## 📦 Deployment\n\nThe site builds as a static export (`output: 'export'`). Deploy the `out/` directory to:\n\n- **Vercel**: Push to GitHub, connect repo\n- **Netlify**: Set build command to `npm run build`, publish directory to `out`\n- **GitHub Pages**: Use the `out/` directory\n- **Any static host**: Upload the `out/` directory\n\n## 🎨 Design\n\n- **Color Palette**: Imperial Red (#C0181F), Dynasty Gold (#D4A017), Ink Black (#1A1008), Parchment (#FDF6E3)\n- **Fonts**: Noto Serif SC (headings), Noto Sans SC (body), IM Fell English (accent)\n\n## ⚙️ Environment Variables\n\n| Variable | Description |\n|----------|-------------|\n| `NEXT_PUBLIC_ORDER_URL` | URL for the online ordering platform |\n\n## 📁 Project Structure\n\n```\napp/\n├── components/\n│   ├── Navigation.tsx    # Sticky nav with mobile hamburger\n│   ├── Hero.tsx          # Full-screen hero with CTAs\n│   ├── MenuHighlights.tsx # Signature dishes grid\n│   ├── OnlineOrderingBanner.tsx # Order CTA banner\n│   ├── About.tsx         # Restaurant story\n│   ├── LocationHours.tsx # Map, address, hours\n│   ├── Contact.tsx       # Contact form\n│   ├── Footer.tsx        # Footer with social links\n│   └── JsonLd.tsx        # SEO structured data\n├── globals.css           # Tailwind + custom styles\n├── layout.tsx            # Root layout with metadata\n└── page.tsx              # Home page\n```\n\n## Tech Stack\n\n- Next.js 16 (App Router)\n- TypeScript\n- Tailwind CSS\n- Static Export\n## 🚀 Production Deployment\n\n### Static Build\nThe site is built as a static export (`output: \"export\"`). The static files are in the `out/` directory after running `npm run build`.\n\n### Deployment Options\n\n#### Option 1: Vercel (Recommended)\n1. Install Vercel CLI: `npm i -g vercel`\n2. Get a token from https://vercel.com/account/tokens\n3. Run: `VERCEL_TOKEN=<token> vercel --prod --yes`\n4. Or connect the GitHub repo at https://vercel.com/new\n\n#### Option 2: Netlify\n1. Install: `npm i -g netlify-cli`\n2. Get a token from https://app.netlify.com/user/applications\n3. Run: `netlify deploy --prod --dir=out --auth=<token>`\n\n#### Option 3: GitHub Pages (requires paid plan for private repos)\nThe `gh-pages` branch is pre-built and ready. Enable GitHub Pages in repo Settings → Pages → Branch: `gh-pages`.\n\n### Custom Domain DNS Setup\n\nTo point **szechuanroyalechinese.com** to your deployment:\n\n#### For Vercel:\nAdd to your DNS registrar:\n```\nType: A\nName: @\nValue: 76.76.21.21\n\nType: CNAME\nName: www\nValue: cname.vercel-dns.com\n```\n\n#### For Netlify:\nAdd to your DNS registrar:\n```\nType: CNAME\nName: @  (or use ALIAS/ANAME if available)\nValue: <your-site-name>.netlify.app\n\nType: CNAME\nName: www\nValue: <your-site-name>.netlify.app\n```\n\nThen add the custom domain in your Vercel/Netlify dashboard under project Settings → Domains.\n","stderr":"","aggregated_output":"# Szechuan Royale Chinese Restaurant Website\n\nA production-ready restaurant website built with Next.js 16, TypeScript, and Tailwind CSS.\n\n## 🏮 Features\n\n- **Mobile-first responsive design** with sticky navigation\n- **Full sections**: Hero, Menu Highlights, Online Ordering CTA, About, Location & Hours, Contact, Footer\n- **Szechuan Chinese aesthetic**: Imperial Red & Dynasty Gold color palette\n- **SEO optimized**: Meta tags, Open Graph, JSON-LD Restaurant schema\n- **Static export** for easy deployment to any hosting platform\n- **Google Fonts**: Noto Serif SC, Noto Sans SC, IM Fell English\n\n## 🚀 Getting Started\n\n```bash\n# Install dependencies\nnpm install\n\n# Run development server\nnpm run dev\n\n# Build for production (static export)\nnpm run build\n\n# The static site is generated in the `out/` directory\n```\n\n## 📦 Deployment\n\nThe site builds as a static export (`output: 'export'`). Deploy the `out/` directory to:\n\n- **Vercel**: Push to GitHub, connect repo\n- **Netlify**: Set build command to `npm run build`, publish directory to `out`\n- **GitHub Pages**: Use the `out/` directory\n- **Any static host**: Upload the `out/` directory\n\n## 🎨 Design\n\n- **Color Palette**: Imperial Red (#C0181F), Dynasty Gold (#D4A017), Ink Black (#1A1008), Parchment (#FDF6E3)\n- **Fonts**: Noto Serif SC (headings), Noto Sans SC (body), IM Fell English (accent)\n\n## ⚙️ Environment Variables\n\n| Variable | Description |\n|----------|-------------|\n| `NEXT_PUBLIC_ORDER_URL` | URL for the online ordering platform |\n\n## 📁 Project Structure\n\n```\napp/\n├── components/\n│   ├── Navigation.tsx    # Sticky nav with mobile hamburger\n│   ├── Hero.tsx          # Full-screen hero with CTAs\n│   ├── MenuHighlights.tsx # Signature dishes grid\n│   ├── OnlineOrderingBanner.tsx # Order CTA banner\n│   ├── About.tsx         # Restaurant story\n│   ├── LocationHours.tsx # Map, address, hours\n│   ├── Contact.tsx       # Contact form\n│   ├── Footer.tsx        # Footer with social links\n│   └── JsonLd.tsx        # SEO structured data\n├── globals.css           # Tailwind + custom styles\n├── layout.tsx            # Root layout with metadata\n└── page.tsx              # Home page\n```\n\n## Tech Stack\n\n- Next.js 16 (App Router)\n- TypeScript\n- Tailwind CSS\n- Static Export\n## 🚀 Production Deployment\n\n### Static Build\nThe site is built as a static export (`output: \"export\"`). The static files are in the `out/` directory after running `npm run build`.\n\n### Deployment Options\n\n#### Option 1: Vercel (Recommended)\n1. Install Vercel CLI: `npm i -g vercel`\n2. Get a token from https://vercel.com/account/tokens\n3. Run: `VERCEL_TOKEN=<token> vercel --prod --yes`\n4. Or connect the GitHub repo at https://vercel.com/new\n\n#### Option 2: Netlify\n1. Install: `npm i -g netlify-cli`\n2. Get a token from https://app.netlify.com/user/applications\n3. Run: `netlify deploy --prod --dir=out --auth=<token>`\n\n#### Option 3: GitHub Pages (requires paid plan for private repos)\nThe `gh-pages` branch is pre-built and ready. Enable GitHub Pages in repo Settings → Pages → Branch: `gh-pages`.\n\n### Custom Domain DNS Setup\n\nTo point **szechuanroyalechinese.com** to your deployment:\n\n#### For Vercel:\nAdd to your DNS registrar:\n```\nType: A\nName: @\nValue: 76.76.21.21\n\nType: CNAME\nName: www\nValue: cname.vercel-dns.com\n```\n\n#### For Netlify:\nAdd to your DNS registrar:\n```\nType: CNAME\nName: @  (or use ALIAS/ANAME if available)\nValue: <your-site-name>.netlify.app\n\nType: CNAME\nName: www\nValue: <your-site-name>.netlify.app\n```\n\nThen add the custom domain in your Vercel/Netlify dashboard under project Settings → Domains.\n","exit_code":0,"duration":{"secs":0,"nanos":51210882},"formatted_output":"# Szechuan Royale Chinese Restaurant Website\n\nA production-ready restaurant website built with Next.js 16, TypeScript, and Tailwind CSS.\n\n## 🏮 Features\n\n- **Mobile-first responsive design** with sticky navigation\n- **Full sections**: Hero, Menu Highlights, Online Ordering CTA, About, Location & Hours, Contact, Footer\n- **Szechuan Chinese aesthetic**: Imperial Red & Dynasty Gold color palette\n- **SEO optimized**: Meta tags, Open Graph, JSON-LD Restaurant schema\n- **Static export** for easy deployment to any hosting platform\n- **Google Fonts**: Noto Serif SC, Noto Sans SC, IM Fell English\n\n## 🚀 Getting Started\n\n```bash\n# Install dependencies\nnpm install\n\n# Run development server\nnpm run dev\n\n# Build for production (static export)\nnpm run build\n\n# The static site is generated in the `out/` directory\n```\n\n## 📦 Deployment\n\nThe site builds as a static export (`output: 'export'`). Deploy the `out/` directory to:\n\n- **Vercel**: Push to GitHub, connect repo\n- **Netlify**: Set build command to `npm run build`, publish directory to `out`\n- **GitHub Pages**: Use the `out/` directory\n- **Any static host**: Upload the `out/` directory\n\n## 🎨 Design\n\n- **Color Palette**: Imperial Red (#C0181F), Dynasty Gold (#D4A017), Ink Black (#1A1008), Parchment (#FDF6E3)\n- **Fonts**: Noto Serif SC (headings), Noto Sans SC (body), IM Fell English (accent)\n\n## ⚙️ Environment Variables\n\n| Variable | Description |\n|----------|-------------|\n| `NEXT_PUBLIC_ORDER_URL` | URL for the online ordering platform |\n\n## 📁 Project Structure\n\n```\napp/\n├── components/\n│   ├── Navigation.tsx    # Sticky nav with mobile hamburger\n│   ├── Hero.tsx          # Full-screen hero with CTAs\n│   ├── MenuHighlights.tsx # Signature dishes grid\n│   ├── OnlineOrderingBanner.tsx # Order CTA banner\n│   ├── About.tsx         # Restaurant story\n│   ├── LocationHours.tsx # Map, address, hours\n│   ├── Contact.tsx       # Contact form\n│   ├── Footer.tsx        # Footer with social links\n│   └── JsonLd.tsx        # SEO structured data\n├── globals.css           # Tailwind + custom styles\n├── layout.tsx            # Root layout with metadata\n└── page.tsx              # Home page\n```\n\n## Tech Stack\n\n- Next.js 16 (App Router)\n- TypeScript\n- Tailwind CSS\n- Static Export\n## 🚀 Production Deployment\n\n### Static Build\nThe site is built as a static export (`output: \"export\"`). The static files are in the `out/` directory after running `npm run build`.\n\n### Deployment Options\n\n#### Option 1: Vercel (Recommended)\n1. Install Vercel CLI: `npm i -g vercel`\n2. Get a token from https://vercel.com/account/tokens\n3. Run: `VERCEL_TOKEN=<token> vercel --prod --yes`\n4. Or connect the GitHub repo at https://vercel.com/new\n\n#### Option 2: Netlify\n1. Install: `npm i -g netlify-cli`\n2. Get a token from https://app.netlify.com/user/applications\n3. Run: `netlify deploy --prod --dir=out --auth=<token>`\n\n#### Option 3: GitHub Pages (requires paid plan for private repos)\nThe `gh-pages` branch is pre-built and ready. Enable GitHub Pages in repo Settings → Pages → Branch: `gh-pages`.\n\n### Custom Domain DNS Setup\n\nTo point **szechuanroyalechinese.com** to your deployment:\n\n#### For Vercel:\nAdd to your DNS registrar:\n```\nType: A\nName: @\nValue: 76.76.21.21\n\nType: CNAME\nName: www\nValue: cname.vercel-dns.com\n```\n\n#### For Netlify:\nAdd to your DNS registrar:\n```\nType: CNAME\nName: @  (or use ALIAS/ANAME if available)\nValue: <your-site-name>.netlify.app\n\nType: CNAME\nName: www\nValue: <your-site-name>.netlify.app\n```\n\nThen add the custom domain in your Vercel/Netlify dashboard under project Settings → Domains.\n","status":"completed"}}}}
{"jsonrpc":"2.0","method":"session/update","params":{"sessionId":"019d4438-400e-7661-b283-c84db8e24803","update":{"sessionUpdate":"tool_call_update","toolCallId":"call_X4vpJ6V0XEDuF5rmaDwKaPB5","status":"completed","rawOutput":{"call_id":"call_X4vpJ6V0XEDuF5rmaDwKaPB5","process_id":"43056","turn_id":"019d4438-401f-7133-9a7b-e968f581165b","command":["/bin/bash","-lc","sed -n '1,260p' app/globals.css"],"cwd":"/tmp/orchestra-workspaces/ws-1774964648433-svlpcp","parsed_cmd":[{"type":"read","cmd":"sed -n '1,260p' app/globals.css","name":"globals.css","path":"app/globals.css"}],"source":"unified_exec_startup","stdout":"@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,600;0,700;0,900;1,400;1,600;1,700&family=Noto+Serif+SC:wght@400;600;700&family=Noto+Sans+SC:wght@300;400;500&display=swap');\n@import \"tailwindcss\";\n\n/* ======== TAILWIND v4 THEME ======== */\n@theme {\n  --color-imperial:     #CC1100;\n  --color-imperial-dk:  #8B0000;\n  --color-gold:         #D4AF37;\n  --color-gold-bright:  #F0C040;\n  --color-bright-gold:  #F0C040;\n  --color-ink:          #0d0806;\n  --color-ink-warm:     #1a0e08;\n  --color-ink-light:    #291510;\n  --color-cream:        #F5E6C8;\n  --color-stone:        #8A7968;\n  --color-stone-lt:     #B8A897;\n  --color-parchment:    #FDF6E3;\n  --color-jade:         #2E7D4F;\n\n  --font-display: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;\n  --font-serif:   'Noto Serif SC', serif;\n  --font-sans:    'Noto Sans SC', sans-serif;\n}\n\nhtml {\n  scroll-behavior: smooth;\n}\n\nbody {\n  background-color: #0d0806;\n  color: #F5E6C8;\n  font-family: 'Noto Sans SC', sans-serif;\n  line-height: 1.7;\n  -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\n}\n\n/* ======== TYPOGRAPHY ======== */\n.font-display { font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif; }\n.font-serif   { font-family: 'Noto Serif SC', serif; }\n.font-sans    { font-family: 'Noto Sans SC', sans-serif; }\n\n/* ======== COLOR UTILITIES ======== */\n.text-gold        { color: #D4AF37; }\n.text-gold-bright { color: #F0C040; }\n.text-crimson     { color: #CC1100; }\n.text-crimson-dk  { color: #8B0000; }\n.text-cream       { color: #F5E6C8; }\n.text-stone       { color: #8A7968; }\n.text-stone-lt    { color: #B8A897; }\n\n.bg-ink       { background-color: #0d0806; }\n.bg-ink-warm  { background-color: #1a0e08; }\n.bg-ink-light { background-color: #291510; }\n.bg-crimson   { background-color: #CC1100; }\n.bg-gold      { background-color: #D4AF37; }\n\n.border-gold      { border-color: #D4AF37; }\n.border-gold-dim  { border-color: rgba(212,175,55,0.3); }\n.border-crimson   { border-color: #CC1100; }\n\n/* ======== CHINESE LATTICE PATTERN ======== */\n.pattern-lattice {\n  background-image:\n    repeating-linear-gradient(0deg, transparent, transparent 19px, rgba(212,175,55,0.05) 19px, rgba(212,175,55,0.05) 20px),\n    repeating-linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, transparent 19px, rgba(212,175,55,0.05) 19px, rgba(212,175,55,0.05) 20px);\n}\n\n.pattern-diamond {\n  background-image:\n    repeating-linear-gradient(45deg, transparent, transparent 12px, rgba(212,175,55,0.04) 12px, rgba(212,175,55,0.04) 13px),\n    repeating-linear-gradient(-45deg, transparent, transparent 12px, rgba(212,175,55,0.04) 12px, rgba(212,175,55,0.04) 13px);\n}\n\n/* ======== ANIMATIONS ======== */\n@keyframes shimmer {\n  0%   { background-position: -200% center; }\n  100% { background-position: 200% center; }\n}\n\n@keyframes fadeUp {\n  from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(28px); }\n  to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }\n}\n\n@keyframes fadeIn {\n  from { opacity: 0; }\n  to   { opacity: 1; }\n}\n\n@keyframes lanternSway {\n  0%, 100% { transform: rotate(-1.5deg) translateY(0); }\n  50%       { transform: rotate(1.5deg) translateY(-4px); }\n}\n\n@keyframes goldPulse {\n  0%, 100% { opacity: 0.6; }\n  50%       { opacity: 1; }\n}\n\n.animate-fade-up  { animation: fadeUp 0.9s cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1) forwards; }\n.animate-fade-in  { animation: fadeIn 1s ease-out forwards; }\n.animate-lantern  { animation: lanternSway 5s ease-in-out infinite; }\n.animate-shimmer  { animation: shimmer 5s linear infinite; }\n\n/* Staggered fade-up */\n.anim-d1 { animation-delay: 0.1s;  opacity: 0; }\n.anim-d2 { animation-delay: 0.28s; opacity: 0; }\n.anim-d3 { animation-delay: 0.46s; opacity: 0; }\n.anim-d4 { animation-delay: 0.62s; opacity: 0; }\n.anim-d5 { animation-delay: 0.78s; opacity: 0; }\n\n/* Gold shimmer text */\n.text-shimmer {\n  background: linear-gradient(90deg, #B8920A 0%, #D4AF37 25%, #F0C040 50%, #D4AF37 75%, #B8920A 100%);\n  background-size: 200% auto;\n  -webkit-background-clip: text;\n  -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;\n  background-clip: text;\n  animation: shimmer 5s linear infinite;\n}\n\n/* ======== BUTTONS ======== */\n.btn-crimson {\n  background-color: #9B0F00;\n  color: #F5E6C8;\n  padding: 0.75rem 2rem;\n  font-family: 'Noto Sans SC', sans-serif;\n  font-weight: 500;\n  letter-spacing: 0.12em;\n  text-transform: uppercase;\n  font-size: 0.8125rem;\n  transition: background-color 0.25s ease, transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.25s ease;\n  display: inline-block;\n  border: 1px solid rgba(204,17,0,0.5);\n  position: relative;\n  overflow: hidden;\n}\n.btn-crimson::after {\n  content: '';\n  position: absolute;\n  inset: 0;\n  background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.07) 0%, transparent 60%);\n  pointer-events: none;\n}\n.btn-crimson:hover {\n  background-color: #CC1100;\n  border-color: rgba(204,17,0,0.8);\n  transform: translateY(-1px);\n  box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(204,17,0,0.35);\n}\n\n.btn-gold-outline {\n  border: 1px solid rgba(212,175,55,0.65);\n  color: #D4AF37;\n  padding: 0.75rem 2rem;\n  font-family: 'Noto Sans SC', sans-serif;\n  font-weight: 500;\n  letter-spacing: 0.12em;\n  text-transform: uppercase;\n  font-size: 0.8125rem;\n  transition: background-color 0.25s ease, color 0.25s ease, transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.25s ease, border-color 0.25s ease;\n  display: inline-block;\n  background: transparent;\n}\n.btn-gold-outline:hover {\n  background-color: rgba(212,175,55,0.1);\n  border-color: #D4AF37;\n  color: #F0C040;\n  transform: translateY(-1px);\n  box-shadow: 0 4px 18px rgba(212,175,55,0.18);\n}\n\n/* ======== MENU CARDS ======== */\n.menu-card {\n  background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(26,14,8,0.9) 0%, rgba(41,21,16,0.5) 100%);\n  border: 1px solid rgba(212,175,55,0.1);\n  transition: border-color 0.25s ease, background 0.25s ease, transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.25s ease;\n}\n.menu-card:hover {\n  border-color: rgba(212,175,55,0.38);\n  transform: translateY(-1px);\n  box-shadow: 0 6px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);\n}\n\n.menu-card-popular {\n  background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(155,15,0,0.15) 0%, rgba(26,14,8,0.9) 100%);\n  border: 1px solid rgba(204,17,0,0.28);\n}\n.menu-card-popular:hover {\n  border-color: rgba(204,17,0,0.5);\n  box-shadow: 0 6px 24px rgba(204,17,0,0.18);\n}\n\n/* ======== GALLERY ======== */\n.gallery-item {\n  overflow: hidden;\n  position: relative;\n}\n.gallery-item img {\n  transition: transform 0.7s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.46, 0.45, 0.94);\n  display: block;\n  width: 100%;\n  height: 100%;\n  object-fit: cover;\n}\n.gallery-item:hover img {\n  transform: scale(1.07);\n}\n.gallery-overlay {\n  position: absolute;\n  inset: 0;\n  background: rgba(139,0,0,0);\n  transition: background 0.4s ease;\n}\n.gallery-item:hover .gallery-overlay {\n  background: rgba(139,0,0,0.22);\n}\n\n/* ======== NAV LINK ======== */\n.nav-link {\n  color: #8A7968;\n  font-size: 0.75rem;\n  letter-spacing: 0.18em;\n  text-transform: uppercase;\n  font-family: 'Noto Sans SC', sans-serif;\n  transition: color 0.25s ease;\n  position: relative;\n}\n.nav-link::after {\n  content: '';\n  position: absolute;\n  bottom: -4px;\n  left: 0;\n  width: 0;\n  height: 1px;\n  background-color: #D4AF37;\n  transition: width 0.3s ease;\n}\n.nav-link:hover {\n  color: #D4AF37;\n}\n.nav-link:hover::after {\n  width: 100%;\n}\n\n/